  "title": "Project Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Main contractor for LTA project seeking for the above\nposition:-</strong></p><p><strong>Alternate Saturday</strong></p><p><u><em><strong>Jobs & Duties:-</strong></em></u></p><ul><li>Assess\n     potential risks, materials and costs</li><li>Responsible\n     to ensure that all materials used, and work performed are in accordance\n     with the specifications & budget.</li><li>Provide\n     advice and resolve creatively any emerging problems/deficiencies</li><li>Supervise\n     the sub contractors work on site</li><li>Handle\n     over the resulting structures and services for use</li><li>Monitor\n     progress and compile reports in project status</li><li>Manage\n     budget and purchase equipment/materials</li><li>Comply\n     with guidelines and regulations including permits, safety etc and deliver\n     technical files and other technical documentation as required]</li><li>Problems\n     solving</li><li>Make\n     sure the site work is on schedule.</li><li>Coordination\n     work with authorities, clients & QP</li></ul><p><u><em>Requirement:-</em></u></p><ul><li>Minimum\n     Degree Holder in Civil Engineering (Recognized by PE Board)</li><li>Minimum\n     8 years and above experience</li><li>Able\n     to work as a team</li><li>Organization/problems\n     solving skills</li></ul>",
